About this hotel

A 5-minute walk from the renowned Majorelle Garden and museum, this relaxed hotel on the corner of a main street is 3 km from both the Marrakech Museum and the lively Jemaa el-Fnaa plaza.

    About this hotel

    A 5-minute walk from the renowned Majorelle Garden and museum, this relaxed hotel on the corner of a main street is 3 km from both the Marrakech Museum and the lively Jemaa el-Fnaa plaza. …

    Colorful, warmly decorated rooms with wood furnishings provide TVs and air-conditioning, as well as en suite bathrooms and safes. Suites add separate sitting areas. Some quarters feature balconies.

    Breakfast is included. There's also a casual eatery with high ceilings and a colorful tile floor, as well as a plant-shaded terrace featuring cafe tables. The hotel does not serve alcohol.
